@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### Realtime reminder
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### How to test Socket.IO manually
# 1. Connect a Socket.IO client to ws://localhost:3000
# 2. Emit event: chat:join
# 3. Payload: { "conversationId": 1 }
# 4. Create a message with messages.http
# 5. Listen for event: message:new
